547
00:30:56,000 --> 00:30:57,519
[SPEAKER_00] sestre plakale,

548
00:30:57,519 --> 00:30:58,640
[SPEAKER_00] Isus se sažalio

549
00:30:58,640 --> 00:31:00,480
[SPEAKER_00] i digao ga iz mrtvih.

550
00:31:00,480 --> 00:31:02,519
[SPEAKER_00] Pa onda bi morao svakog di do toga.

551
00:31:02,519 --> 00:31:03,980
[SPEAKER_00] Nitko ne pjeva kad neka umri.

552
00:31:03,980 --> 00:31:04,859
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da, da, da.

553
00:31:04,859 --> 00:31:05,839
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, nitko ne pjeva,

554
00:31:05,839 --> 00:31:08,180
[SPEAKER_00] nego ga dođe i diže.

555
00:31:08,180 --> 00:31:09,700
[SPEAKER_00] Ja vjerujem

556
00:31:09,700 --> 00:31:14,400
[SPEAKER_00] da je Isus digao Lazara iz mrtvih

557
00:31:14,400 --> 00:31:16,700
[SPEAKER_00] iz razloga toga da pokaže

558
00:31:16,700 --> 00:31:21,400
[SPEAKER_00] da kako treba biti poduzetnik,

559
00:31:21,839 --> 00:31:23,140
[SPEAKER_00] kako treba biti

560
00:31:23,140 --> 00:31:26,319
[SPEAKER_00] stvarati kapital časno i pošteno,

561
00:31:26,319 --> 00:31:29,380
[SPEAKER_00] jer znamo da je ljude koje su usretao,

562
00:31:29,380 --> 00:31:30,279
[SPEAKER_00] žene koje su,

563
00:31:30,279 --> 00:31:31,680
[SPEAKER_00] bila da je slao njima

564
00:31:31,680 --> 00:31:33,759
[SPEAKER_00] kod Lazara na tom.

565
00:31:33,759 --> 00:31:36,799
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ako je iz moj kuta,

566
00:31:36,799 --> 00:31:38,480
[SPEAKER_00] možda ja to želim tako da vidim,

567
00:31:38,480 --> 00:31:41,039
[SPEAKER_00] ili to, možda se neće složiti

568
00:31:41,039 --> 00:31:43,500
[SPEAKER_00] učinjaci duhovni sa mnom,

569
00:31:43,500 --> 00:31:44,400
[SPEAKER_00] ali ja vjerujem

570
00:31:44,400 --> 00:31:47,460
[SPEAKER_00] da je Isus Lazara uskrsnuo

571
00:31:47,460 --> 00:31:49,440
[SPEAKER_00] sa ciljem da pokaže

572
00:31:49,440 --> 00:31:51,720
[SPEAKER_00] vertikalu poduzetnika.

573
00:31:51,839 --> 00:31:55,059
[SPEAKER_00] da pokaže nama kao jednu matricu,

574
00:31:55,059 --> 00:31:58,039
[SPEAKER_00] kao jedan uzor koji će se,

575
00:31:58,039 --> 00:32:00,599
[SPEAKER_00] ali ono što je bitno,

576
00:32:00,599 --> 00:32:02,880
[SPEAKER_00] hršćanstvo nije protiv kapitala.

577
00:32:02,880 --> 00:32:09,319
[SPEAKER_00] Niti protiv poduzetništva.

578
00:32:09,319 --> 00:32:11,759
[SPEAKER_01] Ja bi tu dodao da, recimo,

579
00:32:11,759 --> 00:32:13,839
[SPEAKER_01] mislim sad mi je palo na pamet,

580
00:32:13,839 --> 00:32:15,799
[SPEAKER_01] kažem kad malo analiziraš

581
00:32:15,799 --> 00:32:18,299
[SPEAKER_01] taj dio evanđelja,

582
00:32:18,299 --> 00:32:20,700
[SPEAKER_01] mislim u konačnici Petar je bio poduzetnik.

583
00:32:20,960 --> 00:32:22,059
[SPEAKER_01] imao je radnike.

584
00:32:22,059 --> 00:32:24,440
[SPEAKER_01] Josip je bio poduzetnik.

585
00:32:24,440 --> 00:32:25,019
[UNKNOWN] Tako je.

586
00:32:25,019 --> 00:32:26,019
[SPEAKER_01] On je bio poduzetnik.

587
00:32:26,019 --> 00:32:28,880
[SPEAKER_01] Također, u stvari kad mate je bio poduzetnik.

588
00:32:28,880 --> 00:32:31,259
[SPEAKER_01] Danas je to, nazovemo to tako,

589
00:32:31,259 --> 00:32:34,240
[SPEAKER_01] ono što se bavio je ova agencija za naplatu potrživanja.

590
00:32:34,240 --> 00:32:37,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ali sad malo kad bolje pogledaš,

591
00:32:37,960 --> 00:32:41,500
[SPEAKER_01] u stvari većina njih su bili poduzetnici

592
00:32:41,500 --> 00:32:42,519
[SPEAKER_01] oko Isusa.

593
00:32:43,240 --> 00:32:44,059
[SPEAKER_00] Upravo to.

594
00:32:44,059 --> 00:32:46,680
[SPEAKER_00] I onda nadolazimo na onu jednu

595
00:32:46,680 --> 00:32:48,299
[SPEAKER_00] da pojentira,

596
00:32:48,299 --> 00:32:50,039
[SPEAKER_00] ne bacaj biseri pre svinje.

597
00:32:50,039 --> 00:32:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] Što bi bilo da nitko ne stvara

598
00:32:52,000 --> 00:32:53,200
[SPEAKER_00] novu vrijednost,

599
00:32:53,200 --> 00:32:54,059
[SPEAKER_00] da ne vodi brigo,

600
00:32:54,059 --> 00:32:55,119
[SPEAKER_00] svi imamo neki talent.

601
00:32:55,119 --> 00:32:56,980
[SPEAKER_00] Što bi bilo

602
00:32:56,980 --> 00:32:58,759
[SPEAKER_00] sa ljudima koji nemaju talent

603
00:32:58,759 --> 00:32:59,759
[SPEAKER_00] za priživljavanje,

604
00:32:59,759 --> 00:33:00,920
[SPEAKER_00] za stvaranje novih,

605
00:33:00,920 --> 00:33:03,299
[SPEAKER_00] kojima trebaš obezbijediti radno mjesto?

606
00:33:03,299 --> 00:33:05,680
[SPEAKER_00] Kapital nije problem.

607
00:33:05,680 --> 00:33:07,460
[SPEAKER_00] Sam po sebi.

608
00:33:08,099 --> 00:33:10,480
[SPEAKER_00] Kažu, onda se pojavile mantre

609
00:33:10,480 --> 00:33:11,579
[SPEAKER_00] koje je kakve kapital,

610
00:33:11,579 --> 00:33:13,039
[SPEAKER_00] novac, kvari ljude.

611
00:33:13,039 --> 00:33:14,839
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, to nije istina.

612
00:33:14,839 --> 00:33:18,299
[SPEAKER_00] On samo ističe njihovo lice.

613
00:33:18,299 --> 00:33:21,160
[SPEAKER_00] Ono samo pojačava ono.

614
00:33:21,160 --> 00:33:22,920
[SPEAKER_00] On nije bio u prigodi do sada,

615
00:33:22,920 --> 00:33:24,779
[SPEAKER_00] nije bio u pečatnji.

616
00:33:24,779 --> 00:33:25,940
[SPEAKER_00] On je bio uvijek,

617
00:33:25,940 --> 00:33:26,740
[SPEAKER_00] kako smijem reći,

618
00:33:26,740 --> 00:33:28,640
[SPEAKER_00] sada sam malo o emocijima,

619
00:33:28,640 --> 00:33:29,779
[SPEAKER_00] on je bio uvijek fukara.

620
00:33:29,779 --> 00:33:31,740
[SPEAKER_00] I sada kada je došao

621
00:33:31,740 --> 00:33:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] u poziciju da ima kapital,

622
00:33:34,000 --> 00:33:35,799
[SPEAKER_00] samo je to javno pokazao.

623
00:33:35,799 --> 00:33:36,559
[SPEAKER_00] Niš drugo.

624
00:33:36,559 --> 00:33:37,640
[SPEAKER_00] E, bravo, da, da.

625
00:33:37,640 --> 00:33:39,660
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, to je recimo

626
00:33:39,660 --> 00:33:40,759
[SPEAKER_01] kojeren reflektor

627
00:33:40,759 --> 00:33:42,880
[SPEAKER_01] koji te osvijetli

628
00:33:42,880 --> 00:33:44,079
[SPEAKER_01] u trenutku

629
00:33:44,079 --> 00:33:45,700
[SPEAKER_01] kad dođeš u njevo posliju.

630
00:33:45,700 --> 00:33:46,440
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je.

631
00:33:46,440 --> 00:33:47,059
[SPEAKER_00] Upravo to.

632
00:33:47,059 --> 00:33:48,200
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, upravo to.

633
00:33:48,200 --> 00:33:49,180
[SPEAKER_00] Upravo to.

634
00:33:49,180 --> 00:33:49,759
[SPEAKER_00] Jer,

635
00:33:49,759 --> 00:33:52,819
[SPEAKER_00] što je bit?

636
00:33:52,819 --> 00:33:56,559
[SPEAKER_00] Što je poanta?

637
00:33:56,559 --> 00:33:57,339
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže,

638
00:33:57,339 --> 00:34:00,220
[SPEAKER_00] Einstein je fantastično odgovorio.

639
00:34:00,220 --> 00:34:00,900
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže,

640
00:34:00,900 --> 00:34:02,420
[SPEAKER_00] zlo ne postoji.

641
00:34:02,420 --> 00:34:04,559
[SPEAKER_00] Kako zlo ne postoji?

642
00:34:04,559 --> 00:34:05,660
[SPEAKER_00] Mi kažemo da zlo ne postoji.

643
00:34:05,660 --> 00:34:05,900
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da, da.

644
00:34:05,900 --> 00:34:07,519
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže, mrak ne postoji.

645
00:34:07,619 --> 00:34:08,840
[SPEAKER_00] kako mrak,

646
00:34:08,840 --> 00:34:09,780
[SPEAKER_00] kada je on definirao

647
00:34:09,780 --> 00:34:11,860
[SPEAKER_00] svojom profesoru,

648
00:34:11,860 --> 00:34:12,980
[SPEAKER_00] je li bo postoji?

649
00:34:12,980 --> 00:34:13,780
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ću parafrizirat

650
00:34:13,780 --> 00:34:15,539
[SPEAKER_00] da ne gubimo vrijeme

651
00:34:15,539 --> 00:34:16,219
[SPEAKER_00] na to.

652
00:34:16,219 --> 00:34:16,940
[SPEAKER_00] Znači,

653
00:34:16,940 --> 00:34:20,199
[SPEAKER_00] mi ne možemo mrak izmjeriti.

654
00:34:20,199 --> 00:34:21,199
[SPEAKER_00] Tamo.

655
00:34:21,199 --> 00:34:22,219
[SPEAKER_00] Mi to ne možemo.

656
00:34:22,219 --> 00:34:24,039
[SPEAKER_00] Mi mjerimo svjetlost,

657
00:34:24,039 --> 00:34:24,460
[SPEAKER_00] lukse.

658
00:34:24,860 --> 00:34:25,480
[SPEAKER_00] da, da, da, da.

659
00:34:25,480 --> 00:34:28,019
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, tamo je osutno svjetlosti.

660
00:34:28,239 --> 00:34:28,619
[SPEAKER_01] točno.

661
00:34:28,619 --> 00:34:29,500
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je zlo.

662
00:34:29,500 --> 00:34:30,920
[SPEAKER_00] zlo, zlo samo po sebi

663
00:34:30,920 --> 00:34:33,300
[SPEAKER_00] je samo osutnost dobrote.

664
00:34:33,360 --> 00:34:34,199
[SPEAKER_00] ničega više.

665
00:34:34,199 --> 00:34:35,840
[SPEAKER_00] Zlo samo po sebi.

666
00:34:35,940 --> 00:34:36,820
[SPEAKER_00] jer da nema dobrote,

667
00:34:36,820 --> 00:34:38,159
[SPEAKER_00] da nema svjetlosti,

668
00:34:38,159 --> 00:34:38,900
[SPEAKER_00] bila bi tama,

669
00:34:38,900 --> 00:34:41,480
[SPEAKER_00] bilo bi nešto što ne razumijemo.

670
00:34:42,219 --> 00:34:46,639
[SPEAKER_01] Na tragu poklenog profesora Ivančića

671
00:34:46,639 --> 00:34:48,300
[SPEAKER_01] vezano za vjeru.

672
00:34:48,300 --> 00:34:51,440
[SPEAKER_01] Strah i nedostatak vjera.

673
00:34:51,440 --> 00:34:51,860
[SPEAKER_00] Točno.

674
00:34:51,860 --> 00:34:54,260
[SPEAKER_00] I to je najveći neprijatelj.

675
00:34:54,260 --> 00:34:56,920
[SPEAKER_00] Strah i briga.

676
00:34:56,920 --> 00:34:58,940
[SPEAKER_00] Za nešto što ne možeš utjecati

677
00:34:58,940 --> 00:35:00,380
[SPEAKER_00] i ne zna što će li se uopće dogoditi.

678
00:35:00,380 --> 00:35:01,860
[SPEAKER_00] I to nije sa Bože strane.

679
00:35:01,860 --> 00:35:02,559
[SPEAKER_00] To je sigurno.

680
00:35:02,559 --> 00:35:07,360
[SPEAKER_00] Profit je dosta bitan.

681
00:35:07,360 --> 00:35:09,960
[SPEAKER_00] Jer on te održava iznad vode.

682
00:35:10,639 --> 00:35:12,599
[SPEAKER_00] Kako misliš održava iznad vode?

683
00:35:12,599 --> 00:35:13,719
[SPEAKER_00] U kojem kontekstu?

684
00:35:13,719 --> 00:35:15,900
[SPEAKER_00] Da, u slučaju da si poduzetnik,

685
00:35:15,900 --> 00:35:16,880
[SPEAKER_00] a nemaš profita,

686
00:35:16,880 --> 00:35:18,300
[SPEAKER_00] da nisi pozitivan,

687
00:35:18,300 --> 00:35:19,380
[SPEAKER_00] nema tu,

688
00:35:19,380 --> 00:35:20,420
[SPEAKER_00] nema,

689
00:35:20,420 --> 00:35:22,780
[SPEAKER_00] ili si u minusu,

690
00:35:22,780 --> 00:35:23,639
[SPEAKER_00] ili si u plusu.

691
00:35:23,639 --> 00:35:24,199
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da.

692
00:35:24,199 --> 00:35:25,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ako si u minusu,

693
00:35:25,380 --> 00:35:27,860
[SPEAKER_00] nema neutralnosti.

694
00:35:27,860 --> 00:35:29,320
[SPEAKER_00] Ili si u minusu,

695
00:35:29,320 --> 00:35:29,980
[SPEAKER_00] propadaš,

696
00:35:29,980 --> 00:35:30,880
[SPEAKER_00] ili si u plusu,

697
00:35:30,880 --> 00:35:31,539
[SPEAKER_00] ideš dalje.

698
00:35:31,539 --> 00:35:33,480
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, nikada nije problem

699
00:35:33,480 --> 00:35:34,679
[SPEAKER_00] sama po sebi novace.

700
00:35:34,679 --> 00:35:36,980
[SPEAKER_00] Nikada nije profit.

701
00:35:36,980 --> 00:35:39,920
[SPEAKER_00] Cilj je održivost.

702
00:35:40,639 --> 00:35:43,980
[SPEAKER_00] dostojanstvo čovjeka.

703
00:35:43,980 --> 00:35:45,400
[SPEAKER_00] To je cilj.

704
00:35:46,019 --> 00:35:51,440
[SPEAKER_00] a kada shvatiš da je pozicija upravitelja,

705
00:35:51,440 --> 00:35:52,860
[SPEAKER_00] poduzetnika,

706
00:35:52,860 --> 00:35:54,519
[SPEAKER_00] pomoći drugima,

707
00:35:54,519 --> 00:35:56,139
[SPEAKER_00] on samo upravlja,

708
00:35:56,139 --> 00:36:03,559
[SPEAKER_00] sustav prekonoći može uništiti i čovjeka,

709
00:36:03,559 --> 00:36:04,940
[SPEAKER_00] i poduzetnika,

710
00:36:04,940 --> 00:36:06,440
[SPEAKER_00] i bilo što,

711
00:36:06,440 --> 00:36:07,780
[SPEAKER_00] nacionalizacija,

712
00:36:07,780 --> 00:36:08,820
[SPEAKER_00] i tako dalje.

713
00:36:08,820 --> 00:36:09,360
[SPEAKER_00] Tako,

714
00:36:09,360 --> 00:36:11,340
[SPEAKER_00] ako su poduzetnici toga svjesni,

715
00:36:11,340 --> 00:36:12,239
[SPEAKER_00] onda,

716
00:36:12,239 --> 00:36:14,139
[SPEAKER_00] onda rade najbolje što može

717
00:36:14,139 --> 00:36:16,699
[SPEAKER_00] i on će sigurno opet uspjeti,

718
00:36:16,699 --> 00:36:17,440
[SPEAKER_00] ako smijem reći.

719
00:36:18,460 --> 00:36:18,739
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro,

720
00:36:18,739 --> 00:36:19,900
[SPEAKER_01] a daj nam reci,

721
00:36:19,900 --> 00:36:21,579
[SPEAKER_01] iz tvojeg iskustva,

722
00:36:21,579 --> 00:36:23,719
[SPEAKER_01] postoji li razlika u posljedicama,

723
00:36:23,719 --> 00:36:27,519
[SPEAKER_01] kada je kapital stečen korektno,

724
00:36:27,519 --> 00:36:28,559
[SPEAKER_01] na ispravan način,

725
00:36:28,559 --> 00:36:29,679
[SPEAKER_01] možemo to tako reći,

726
00:36:29,679 --> 00:36:30,599
[SPEAKER_01] i transparentno,

727
00:36:30,599 --> 00:36:33,579
[SPEAKER_01] u odnosu na kapital stečen pritiskom,

728
00:36:33,579 --> 00:36:35,079
[SPEAKER_01] ili manipulacijom,

729
00:36:35,800 --> 00:36:37,900
[SPEAKER_01] u tom negativnom kontekstu,

730
00:36:37,900 --> 00:36:38,679
[SPEAKER_01] da tako kažem.

731
00:36:38,679 --> 00:36:39,119
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

732
00:36:39,119 --> 00:36:41,719
[SPEAKER_00] Postoji.

733
00:36:41,719 --> 00:36:43,440
[SPEAKER_00] Postoji logična stvar,

734
00:36:43,440 --> 00:36:45,400
[SPEAKER_00] očekivani odgovor,

735
00:36:45,400 --> 00:36:47,360
[SPEAKER_00] ali vjeruj mi da postoji.

736
00:36:47,360 --> 00:36:48,800
[SPEAKER_00] Postoji,

737
00:36:48,800 --> 00:36:50,900
[SPEAKER_00] i to ne samo moralna,

738
00:36:50,900 --> 00:36:53,599
[SPEAKER_00] nego konkretna i mjernjivo u praksi.

739
00:36:53,599 --> 00:36:59,019
[SPEAKER_00] U ekonomiji postoji ona jedinstvena istina,

740
00:36:59,019 --> 00:37:00,420
[SPEAKER_00] nema besplatnog ručka.

741
00:37:00,420 --> 00:37:05,320
[SPEAKER_00] Nikada nema dovoljno,

742
00:37:05,800 --> 00:37:09,159
[SPEAKER_00] znači prva lekcija u ekonomiji je oskudnost.

743
00:37:09,159 --> 00:37:16,500
[SPEAKER_00] Na zemlji nikada nema ničega dovoljno za sve koji bi to htjeli,

744
00:37:16,500 --> 00:37:18,760
[SPEAKER_00] bez obzira o čemu se radi.

745
00:37:18,760 --> 00:37:23,719
[SPEAKER_00] I sa time moramo i trebamo upravljati racionalno.

746
00:37:23,719 --> 00:37:27,940
[SPEAKER_00] Trebamo upravljati najbolje što možemo,

747
00:37:27,940 --> 00:37:33,800
[SPEAKER_00] i tu kapitalizam, kapital poduzetno postaje ključno.

748
00:37:35,400 --> 00:37:38,539
[SPEAKER_00] iz mog iskustva kada poduzetnik,

749
00:37:38,539 --> 00:37:40,340
[SPEAKER_00] kada je korektan,

750
00:37:40,340 --> 00:37:42,219
[SPEAKER_00] kada je partner sustava,

751
00:37:42,219 --> 00:37:45,900
[SPEAKER_00] kada je partner okoline,

752
00:37:45,900 --> 00:37:47,739
[SPEAKER_00] grada i tako dalje,

753
00:37:47,739 --> 00:37:54,260
[SPEAKER_00] kada je sustav mu to prije ili kasnije vrati,

754
00:37:54,260 --> 00:37:55,519
[SPEAKER_00] ne savršeno,

755
00:37:55,519 --> 00:37:57,159
[SPEAKER_00] ali dovoljno da svi,

756
00:37:57,159 --> 00:37:58,920
[SPEAKER_00] ili barem velika većina,

757
00:37:58,920 --> 00:37:59,739
